---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
import ProseSection from '../components/ProseSection.astro';
import CtaButton from '../components/CtaButton.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Parent Partnership"
  description="At Toddler World, parents and educators work hand in hand. Regular updates, open communication and twice-yearly progress meetings keep you close to your child's journey."
>
  <PageHero eyebrow="You & us, together" title="Parent Partnership" accent="tangerine">
    <p>Because the best outcomes happen when home and school pull in the same direction.</p>
  </PageHero>

  <section class="section container">
    <ProseSection
      image="/images/parentpartnership/1.webp"
      alt="A loving moment between parents and their child"
      accent="tangerine"
      reverse
    >
      <p class="lead">
        The bond between our staff and our parents can never be underestimated, because we all want
        the very same thing: a happy, nurturing atmosphere where your child can flourish.
      </p>
      <p>
        That's why we work hard every single day to give every family excellent care and
        communication, keeping you in the loop at every opportunity, and at every stage of your
        child's development.
      </p>
      <p>
        Formal parent–teacher meetings are scheduled twice a year to review your child's progress
        and achievements, and to set gentle goals for what comes next. And beyond those meetings,
        you're always welcome to reach out to any member of staff whenever you have a question or
        something you'd like to talk through.
      </p>
      <p>
        We provide a range of resources and support so you always feel well informed and completely
        secure in the knowledge that your child is safe, happy and cared for.
      </p>
      <p>
        We'd love you to get involved too, so if you'd like to know more, just ask a member of the
        Toddler World team next time you're here.
      </p>
      <p><strong>Together, we can make a difference.</strong></p>
      <div class="btn-row">
        <CtaButton href="/contact-us">Talk to us</CtaButton>
      </div>
    </ProseSection>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .btn-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--sp-3);
    margin-top: var(--sp-6);
  }
</style>
